{"id":75,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":75,"title":"D&C 71","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 71"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given to Joseph Smith the Prophet and Sidney Rigdon, at Hiram, Ohio, December 1, 1831. The Prophet had continued to translate the Bible with Sidney Rigdon as his scribe until this revelation was received, at which time it was temporarily laid aside so as to enable them to fulfill the instruction given herein. The brethren were to go forth to preach in order to allay the unfriendly feelings that had developed against the Church as a result of the publication of letters written by Ezra Booth, who had apostatized."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.1-4"},"1–4"],", Joseph Smith and Sidney Rigdon are sent forth to proclaim the gospel;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.5-11"},"5–11"],", Enemies of the Saints will be confounded."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.1","order":"06.05.071.8530"},["b","1"],"Behold, thus saith the Lord unto you my servants Joseph Smith, Jun., and Sidney Rigdon, that the time has verily come that it is necessary and expedient in me that you should open your mouths in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"proclaiming"],"my gospel, the things of the kingdom, expounding the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"mysteries"],"thereof out of the scriptures, according to that portion of Spirit and power which shall be given unto you, even as I will."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.2","order":"06.05.071.8531"},["b","2"],"Verily I say unto you, proclaim unto the world in the regions round about, and in the church also, for the space of a season, even until it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"made"],"known unto you."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.3","order":"06.05.071.8532"},["b","3"],"Verily this is a mission for a season, which I give unto you."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.4","order":"06.05.071.8533"},["b","4"],"Wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"labor"],"ye in my vineyard. Call upon the inhabitants of the earth, and bear record, and prepare the way for the commandments and revelations which are to come."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.5","order":"06.05.071.8534"},["b","5"],"Now, behold this is wisdom; whoso readeth, let him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"understand"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"receive"],"also;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.6","order":"06.05.071.8535"},["b","6"],"For unto him that receiveth it shall be given more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"abundantly"],", even power."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.7","order":"06.05.071.8536"},["b","7"],"Wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"confound"],"your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"enemies"],"; call upon them to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"meet"],"you both in public and in private; and inasmuch as ye are faithful their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"shame"],"shall be made manifest."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.8","order":"06.05.071.8537"},["b","8"],"Wherefore, let them bring forth their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"strong reasons"],"against the Lord."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.9","order":"06.05.071.8538"},["b","9"],"Verily, thus saith the Lord unto you—there is no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"weapon"],"that is formed against you shall prosper;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.10","order":"06.05.071.8539"},["b","10"],"And if any man lift his voice against you he shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"confounded"],"in mine own due time."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.11","order":"06.05.071.8540"},["b","11"],"Wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"keep"],"my commandments; they are true and faithful. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.1a","order":"06.05.071.8541"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/4.23"},"Matt. 4:23"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.1b","order":"06.05.071.8543"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.61.61-65"},"D&C 42:61 (61–65)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.2a","order":"06.05.071.8545"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/73.3"},"D&C 73:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.4a","order":"06.05.071.8547"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.19"},"D&C 24:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.5a","order":"06.05.071.8549"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"TG Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.5b","order":"06.05.071.8551"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.10.9-11"},"Alma 12:10 (9–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.6a","order":"06.05.071.8553"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.12"},"Matt. 13:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.7a","order":"06.05.071.8555"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/83.17.2-17"},"Ps. 83:17 (2–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.14"},"2 Ne. 25:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.15.14-16"},"Moses 7:15 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.7b","order":"06.05.071.8557"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/enemies"},"TG Enemies"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.7c","order":"06.05.071.8559"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.37"},"D&C 19:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.47"},"58:47"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.37"},"63:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.8"},"68:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.7d","order":"06.05.071.8561"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.8a","order":"06.05.071.8563"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.21"},"Isa. 41:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.9a","order":"06.05.071.8565"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.17"},"Isa. 54:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.10a","order":"06.05.071.8567"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/17.18.15-18"},"Jer. 17:18 (15–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/71.11a","order":"06.05.071.8569"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.28"},"Ex. 16:28"],"."]]}
